{"word":"ὧδε","slug":"ὧδε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὧδε</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὅδε\">ὅδε</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> of place: marker of a position that is relatively near<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on movement to a point <b>here, to this place, hither <a href='B:470 8:29'>Mt 8:29</a>; <a href='B:470 17:17'>17:17</a>; <a href='B:470 20:6'>20:6</a>; <a href='B:470 22:12'>22:12</a>; <a href='B:480 11:3'>Mk 11:3</a>; <a href='B:490 9:41'>Lk 9:41</a>; <a href='B:500 6:25'>J 6:25</a>; <a href='B:500 20:27'>20:27</a>; <a href='B:730 4:1'>Rv 4:1</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on position at a point <b>here, in this place <a href='B:470 12:6'>Mt 12:6</a>; <a href='B:480 9:1'>Mk 9:1</a>, <a href='B:480 9:5'>5</a>; <a href='B:480 16:6'>16:6</a>; <a href='B:490 4:23'>Lk 4:23</a>; <a href='B:490 11:31'>11:31f</a>; <a href='B:490 17:21'>17:21</a>; <a href='B:490 21:6'>21:6</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:500 6:9'>J 6:9</a>; <a href='B:500 11:21'>11:21</a>; <a href='B:510 9:14'>Ac 9:14</a>; <a href='B:650 13:14'>Hb 13:14</a>; <a href='B:660 2:3'>Js 2:3</a>.</b> <el>τὰ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὧδε\">ὧδε</a></el> matters here <b><a href='B:580 4:9'>Col 4:9</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on a stage in discussion <b>here, in this connection <a href='B:530 4:2'>1 Cor 4:2</a>; <a href='B:730 13:10'>Rv 13:10</a>.</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὧδε\">ὧδε</a> ἡ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σοφία\">σοφία</a> ἐστίν</el> here is where wisdom is required <b><a href='B:730 13:18'>13:18</a>.</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὧδε\">ὧδε</a></el>... <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκεῖ\">ἐκεῖ</a></el> here / in this case... there / in the other case <b><a hr